query: DELETE FROM property_images WHERE id IN (SELECT id FROM (SELECT pi.id, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY pi.image_url ORDER BY pi.id DESC) as row_num FROM property_images pi WHERE pi.image_url IN (SELECT image_url FROM property_images GROUP BY image_url HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT property_id) > 1)) as dup WHERE row_num > 1);
